{"tid":809553,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"其實穆斯林d白色長袍舒唔舒服?","createTime":"2018-09-07T09:22:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T13:04:33.000Z","uid":14737,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"21a99b1898cfd8a944149734f16f00a4ed0bff4b","tid":809553,"uid":14737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T09:22:55.000Z","msg":"有冇伊斯蘭教巴打著過? 又鍾唔鍾意著?<br />\n<br />\n香港夏天熱到仆街, 成日見d咖哩仔著, 好似一滴汗都冇跑黎跑去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果入面係真空應該幾啱夏天著<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係男人老狗著裙實俾人講, 如果宗教原因應該連著返工都ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最多唔係街食豬肉<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打都係咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"329b785a3e296f38f2cd9c89a51e3587c2e3ca5a","tid":809553,"uid":49055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T09:24:53.000Z","msg":"咖喱仔唔係印度咩？ 關穆斯林咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bddd4aee295407c614af22667506c163ce573508","tid":809553,"uid":199902,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T09:27:38.000Z","msg":"望落真係好滑好透氣好舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要係白色唔吸熱<br />\n聽講件袍設計到啲風會又袍底<br />\n即係腳掌位  吹上去袍入面"},{"pid":"a6341cc9872195b4c745c2597bc82318c5ebd446","tid":809553,"uid":14737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"329b785a3e296f38f2cd9c89a51e3587c2e3ca5a","tid":809553,"uid":49055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T09:24:53.000Z","msg":"咖喱仔唔係印度咩？ 關穆斯林咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T09:34:13.000Z","msg":"印度人都有囉, 不過巴打咁堅持, 咁就南亞人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔識分巴基定緬甸定印度<br />\n<br />\n求其google下, 印度人入面穆斯林人數排第二, 僅次於印度教"},{"pid":"3ea867225cba73aa5955dcbeaf3c1509cf830990","tid":809553,"uid":49055,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,